> user
Implement the functionality of the convo.output-tag-write and convo.output-tag-diff for the Convo-Lang
VSCode extension.

The convo.output-tag-write command should first ask the user to confirm they want to overwrite the current file.

The convo.output-tag-diff command should show the user a diff of the current contents of the target file
and the content of the output tag.

If the output tag has the `fenced` boolean attribute the wrapping code fench in the xml tag should
be removed.



